# .gitignore — Shirei Shabbat public-repo policy
#
# WHAT SHIPS (tracked): everything a colleague needs to rebuild and adapt the book.
#   build/                    the zero-network toolchain — vendored Typst tarball
#                             (build/tools/) and vendored OFL fonts (build/fonts/)
#   build/typst/book.typ      the template: palette, rail, helpers, UNITS/CAPTIONS
#   build/typst/shirei-shabbat-FULL.typ   the service order (the whole book)
#   build/typst/content/*.typ the canonical prayer-unit sources
#   liturgy-map/              the why-record: DECISIONS-LOG, CAPTIONS, RITUAL-MARKS…
#   01_STYLE_GUIDE.md         the voice bible (deliberately KEPT — colleagues need it)
#   CLAUDE.md · FORK-YOUR-OWN.md · README.md · LICENSE.md
#
# WHAT STAYS PRIVATE (ignored): internal process docs, worklogs, critiques, dated
# proofs, design experiments — and the licensed Debbie Friedman / Drorah Setel
# Mi Shebeirach setting (build/typst/content/mi-shebeirach-local.typ), which each
# community must license or replace (the committed placeholder explains how).
#
# NOTE: .gitignore does not untrack files that are already committed. The matching
# `git rm -r --cached` pass (and the fresh-history publish step) lives in
# PUBLISH-CHECKLIST.md.

# ---- internal process directories -------------------------------------------
worklog/
research/
critiques/
design-lab/
proofs/

# ---- internal process docs (repo root) --------------------------------------
# Glob forms so future session docs (V9, V10…) can't leak the way a literal
# V8-only list would. (Dry-run 2026-07-07 caught V8-SESSION-STATUS.md slipping
# through the earlier explicit list.)
HANDOFF-*.md
RUN-V*-PROMPT.md
REVISION-PLAN-*.md
*SESSION-STATUS*.md
StartHere.md
00_PROJECT_BRIEF.md
02_CONTENT_PLAN.md
03_MARGIN_SYSTEM_PLAN.md
PROJECT_PLAN.md
KICKOFF_PROMPT.md
DROP_IN_KICKOFF.md
# (01_STYLE_GUIDE.md is intentionally NOT listed here — it ships.)

# ---- the private Mi Shebeirach setting + its build-generated selector -------
# mi-shebeirach-local.typ  = the Friedman/Setel unit, licensed to CRC only
# mi-shebeirach.typ        = one-line selector written by build/setup.sh / check.sh
build/typst/content/mi-shebeirach-local.typ
build/typst/content/mi-shebeirach.typ

# ---- build outputs & scratch -------------------------------------------------
out*.pdf
out*.png
*.tmp
tmp/
build/latex/*.pdf
build/latex/*.log
build/latex/*.aux
build/latex/*.err
build/latex/*.png

# ---- stray sandbox write-test artifacts --------------------------------------
.wtest

# ---- OS junk ------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
NUL

# ---- post-kit session/process files (added at publish time 2026-07-08) -------
publish-kit/
EDITIONS-ARCHITECTURE.md
RESUME-V8-PROMPT.md
RUN-PUBLISH-PROMPT.md
